{
  "texts": [
    "MUS-CLE and hmmbuild were used to build profile hidden Markov models of both sets.",
    "Hmmsearch was used to score each UniProt Ldh_1_ N/Ldh_1_C sequence against the MDH and LDH profiles and sequences that had a stronger match to the MDH profile were retained.",
    "Additional processing was performed exactly as with the round 1 CuSOD data curation.",
    "Quantification of domain architectures.",
    "See the Supplementary Methods."
  ]
}